<activity xml:id="act-unGrupoDePlantulas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>Sample responses:</p><ul>
<li>These measurements are the height of seedlings.</li>
<li>Some lengths are given in half inches.</li>
<li>There are 22 x’s, so 22 seedlings were measured.</li>
<li>Three seedlings were <m>2\frac{1}{2}</m> inches tall.</li>
<li>The shortest seedlings were <m>\frac{1}{2}</m> inch tall.</li>
</ul>
      </li>
      <li><p>Sample responses:</p><ul>
<li>How tall is the tallest seedling that was measured?</li>
<li>How many seedlings were <m>1\frac{1}{2}</m> inches tall?</li>
<li>How many seedlings were taller than 2 inches?</li>
<li>Which seedling height was the most common?</li>
</ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


